Made to know that we do not control our space.

02:10:40.800 --> 02:10:41.360
Yes.

02:10:41.360 --> 02:10:43.520
Do you find that highly credible?

02:10:43.520 --> 02:10:44.080
Yes.

02:10:44.080 --> 02:10:46.400
What percentage?

02:10:46.400 --> 02:10:53.360
A hundred- because it was definitive. It was- that was told to me definitively, not speculatively. It was-

02:10:53.360 --> 02:10:54.560
we know this to be true.

02:10:54.560 --> 02:10:59.520
So I've been told the same thing by multiple parties who are not related, all of whom seem

02:10:59.520 --> 02:11:05.920
like credible people. Yet nobody seems to have direct first-hand-

02:11:05.920 --> 02:11:11.200
Yeah. Even I can't get into that level. I mean, Harry Reid tried to get a special

02:11:11.200 --> 02:11:17.200
access program and he failed because Deputy Secretary of Defense William Lynn denied it. And that was

02:11:17.200 --> 02:11:21.840
because Harry Reid did it the wrong way. He did it the wrong way, and that's why it got denied. If we

02:11:21.840 --> 02:11:28.880
did it the proper way, which I'm trained on in the security apparatus, we would have been more successful.

02:11:28.880 --> 02:11:29.880
So-

02:11:29.880 --> 02:11:32.880
Do you remember Dick Feynman's book of stories, like,

