Surely You're Joking and What Do You Care What Other People Think?

02:11:35.760 --> 02:11:38.160
Oh, yeah. It's been a long time since-

02:11:38.160 --> 02:11:43.200
Do you remember a story called Any Questions, in which he goes to Buffalo, New York, because

02:11:44.000 --> 02:11:49.120
