02:11:49.920 --> 02:11:51.920
Yeah, vaguely. I vaguely remember that.

02:11:51.920 --> 02:11:57.520
So he gets beat up or something in a washroom over a girl, I forget what.

02:11:57.520 --> 02:12:04.400
Do you have a sense what Richard Feynman was doing with all of this? Because he also has

